/08/1970-08-08a.png?resize=124%2C300&amp;ssl=1 124w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08a.png?resize=425%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 425w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08a.png?resize=637%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 637w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 682px) 100vw, 682px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28565\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1970-08-08b-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08b.png?fit=489%2C1759&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"489,1759\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1970-08-08b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08b.png?fit=285%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28565 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08b.png?resize=489%2C1759&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"489\" height=\"1759\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08b.png?w=489&amp;ssl=1 489w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08b.png?resize=83%2C300&amp;ssl=1 83w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08b.png?resize=285%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 285w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08b.png?resize=427%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 427w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 489px) 100vw, 489px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28566\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1970-08-08c-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08c.png?fit=1111%2C1409&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1111,1409\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1970-08-08c\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08c.png?fit=758%2C962&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28566 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08c.png?resize=758%2C961&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"961\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08c.png?w=1111&amp;ssl=1 1111w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08c.png?resize=237%2C300&amp;ssl=1 237w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08c.png?resize=807%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 807w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1970-08-08c.png?resize=768%2C974&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11888\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1970-08-08/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1970-08-08.jpg?fit=421%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"421,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1970-08-08\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1970-08-08.jpg?fit=421%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11888 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1970-08-08.jpg?resize=421%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"421\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1970-08-08.jpg?w=421&amp;ssl=1 421w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1970-08-08.jpg?resize=253%2C300&amp;ssl=1 253w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 421px) 100vw, 421px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce places a famous ad in the Village Voice classifieds. Among the respondents: Roy Bittan and Max Weinberg.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>&#8220;Backstreets&#8221; is played for the first time ever, as the Born to Run Tour begins to pick up steam in Akron, Ohio. &#8220;Then She Kissed Me&#8221; also makes its tour premiere tonight.</p>\n<div id=\"v-D1aamrTq-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/D1aamrTq?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/S9bQHNVtfvA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDS9bQHNVtfvA\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>A planned Darkness Tour stop at Ryserson University in Toronto is cancelled.</p>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Cats on a Smooth Surface on stage at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park for seven songs, including a work-in-progress (and never released) &#8220;On the Prowl&#8221; and covers of &#8220;Ready Teddy,&#8221; &#8220;Come On, Let&#8217;s Go,&#8221; and &#8220;Come On Over to My Place.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-GZQFnl9z-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/GZQFnl9z?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their third of ten nights at the Brendan Byrne Arena in East Rutherford on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour.</p>\n<div id=\"v-qUtloRcX-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/qUtloRcX?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their first of three Rising Tour nights at Lincoln Financial Field in Philadelphia, where fans enjoy the first full-band &#8220;Lost in the Flood&#8221; of the tour.</p>\n<div id=\"v-RC0F6oBf-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/RC0F6oBf?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28569\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-08-08b-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2003-08-08b.png?fit=467%2C1641&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"467,1641\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-08-08b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2003-08-08b.png?fit=291%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28569 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2003-08-08b.png?resize=467%2C1641&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"1641\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2003-08-08b.png?w=467&amp;ssl=1 467w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2003-08-08b.png?resize=85%2C300&amp;ssl=1 85w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2003-08-08b.png?resize=291%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 291w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2003-08-08b.png?resize=437%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 437w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 467px) 100vw, 467px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> resumes its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City after an almost two-week break. In attendance tonight: Kings of Leon drummer Nathan Followell.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28571\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2018-08-08/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2018-08-08.jpg?fit=500%2C497&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,497\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2018-08-08\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-la